    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/4676ffc4469e7b87ab9f632fef33fda3.poster.avif?t=1772092740\" width=620 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/4676ffc4469e7b87ab9f632fef33fda3.webm?t=1772092740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本试玩版仍在积极开发中！我们正在全力以赴，为大家带来最好的《恋人迷局》游戏体验。感谢你的耐心等待，希望你会喜欢这款游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在试玩版中，你将体验故事的前四天，并与主要角色进行互动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >到第四天时，好感度最高的角色将登场，触发对应的支线剧情——但是分支线路将在正式版中才会开放。不过你仍然可以提前一窥转折点之前的剧情走向！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请小心，游戏中藏有几个Bad Ending，注意保持理智值哦～</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款视觉小说 / 乙女游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/f8c59350dcc9a6efa3bbb681490bf43b.poster.avif?t=1772092740\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/f8c59350dcc9a6efa3bbb681490bf43b.webm?t=1772092740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/f8c59350dcc9a6efa3bbb681490bf43b.mp4?t=1772092740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※ 本试玩版共有5天内容，目前中文已完成到第4天，<strong>第5天会以英文显示</strong>。剩下的翻译正在制作中，之后会更新补上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >谢谢大家的耐心等待！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/9db7200ffe9ad6ada453d24cfd1f7435.avif?t=1772092740\" width=620 height=164 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/f7348ca1d1b368f76d32978ce7c94e16.poster.avif?t=1772092740\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/f7348ca1d1b368f76d32978ce7c94e16.webm?t=1772092740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/f7348ca1d1b368f76d32978ce7c94e16.mp4?t=1772092740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/26ea7648a296b7ddf7bfe090b81bfd26.poster.avif?t=1772092740\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/26ea7648a296b7ddf7bfe090b81bfd26.webm?t=1772092740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/26ea7648a296b7ddf7bfe090b81bfd26.mp4?t=1772092740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演一位二十多岁后期的女性，在复杂的人际关系与自身精神状态之间苦苦挣扎，同时试图揭开丈夫离奇死亡背后的真相。你必须在一个充满秘密的网络中前行，面对神秘的邪教组织、过往的心理创伤，以及层层纠葛的关系。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本试玩版包含故事的前四天，你可以探索游戏世界，邂逅各位角色！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/5d5d219901bb28433f889eabb7ccd089.avif?t=1772092740\" width=620 height=164 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/7cb7b1f5734f3e43b8dd93d5af4f34b3.avif?t=1772092740\" width=620 height=114 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在试玩版中，你将会遇见四位男主角，并与他们互动！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/300d1210396b83ca7e19b7ce0ef21452.avif?t=1772092740\" width=800 height=798 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/d5e0b93ee312b4defa32f970a52f7686.avif?t=1772092740\" width=800 height=798 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/f1e0ec65a3d2bafaa27dd9bbf1f6c70e.avif?t=1772092740\" width=800 height=798 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/77fb635921ae6c27809d0eec67944f8a.avif?t=1772092740\" width=800 height=798 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/81856ddefabdf98e0b93791730351db8.avif?t=1772092740\" width=620 height=164 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >正式版内容：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⦁\t多条剧情线路</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⦁\t多种结局等待解锁</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⦁\t丰富的剧情立绘（CG）可供收集</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⦁\t节奏小游戏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >试玩版内容：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⦁\t根据不同男主，总共可解锁8张剧情立绘（CG）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⦁\t5种结局</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⦁\t节奏小游戏</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⦁\t支线剧情体验</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/a58fd5adaaf0c01b0bae1f9e7f068426.poster.avif?t=1772092740\" width=800 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/a58fd5adaaf0c01b0bae1f9e7f068426.webm?t=1772092740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/a58fd5adaaf0c01b0bae1f9e7f068426.mp4?t=1772092740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/6377c90fb48e148888332a0d008de45d.poster.avif?t=1772092740\" width=800 height=416 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/6377c90fb48e148888332a0d008de45d.webm?t=1772092740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/6377c90fb48e148888332a0d008de45d.mp4?t=1772092740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/82062d8a28dd1139e62ff067278f75f6.poster.avif?t=1772092740\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/82062d8a28dd1139e62ff067278f75f6.webm?t=1772092740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/82062d8a28dd1139e62ff067278f75f6.mp4?t=1772092740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/afd7af1825dfd0a7b7b879a5f30e93c6.poster.avif?t=1772092740\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/afd7af1825dfd0a7b7b879a5f30e93c6.webm?t=1772092740\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/afd7af1825dfd0a7b7b879a5f30e93c6.mp4?t=1772092740\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感谢你对游戏的支持，祝你玩得愉快！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras/bcb381612d65e4aceb7961d8fc09d28e.avif?t=1772092740\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3123540/extras_big/bcb381612d65e4aceb7961d8fc09d28e.webp?t=1772092740 width=1560 height=197 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们的 Kickstarter 众筹活动已经结束，但现在参与还不算太晚！目前仍然开放“Late Pledge”（延迟支持），无论是对我们的周边商品感兴趣，还是想参加 2026 年 2 月底的 Beta 测试，都可以参与。如果你正是其中一员，千万不要错过这个机会！</p>",
